  - TutorialPageTitle: Lifeforce Reaction
    TutorialPageTitleWidth: 1110
    DefaultTextLocation: {x: 0, y: 40}
    DefaultText: 'The Alchemist''s passive ability is

      Lifeforce Reaction.
      When a potion

      is picked up it fires a projectile towards

      the
      boss to deal minor damage.'
    TutorialPageObjectLocation: {x: 0, y: 0}
